# Windsurf/Cascade Rules

Context files (required):
- AGENTS.md
- docs/software-overview.md
- docs/limits.md

Rules:
- Work only within defined limits.
- Ask for approval if limits are exceeded.
- Keep changes minimal and traceable.
- Run impacted tests/checks and report results.
- Follow docs/issues structure for issue artifacts.
- Include privacy checklist for personal-data features.
- Use `work_id` format `WK-YYYYMMDD-<short-slug>` in planning docs and commit messages.
- At stage end, update `handoff.md` and `docs/napkin-lessons.md` per `docs/workflows/session-close.md`.
